org.inventivetalent.nicknamer.api

Interface NickManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PluginNickManager, SimpleNickManager

    public interface NickManager
    Note: If you only use the API artifact without the plugin installed, you will only be able to use the refreshPlayer(UUID) methods.

    It's recommended to use the ProfileDisguiseEvents, but you can also use these methods if the plugin is installed
